OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fover north Argyll will soon clear,
OL,7,Fotherwise this evening will be dry
OL,8,Fwith some late sunshine. A dry start
OL,9,Fto the night then thickening cloud
OL,10,Fbrings rain across all parts later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FRain will mostly clear away
OL,13,Fthrough the morning, although some
OL,14,Flight rain will linger into the
OL,15,Fafternoon, mainly over Argyll. Further
OL,16,Frain spreads northeast in the evening.
OL,17,FWarm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
